1
00:00:01,120 --> 00:00:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Generally, the Spirytus 
employees work as torturers.</i></font>

2
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But just for tonight...</i></font>

3
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:15,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for choosing me.</font>

4
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:18,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>...they transform into princes!</i></font>

5
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:46,160
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#171719">The <font color="#d9000d">Daily <font color="#269df2">L<font color="#171719">ife of a <font color="#ef670f">P<font color="#171719">art-Time <font color="#44c10c">T<font color="#171719">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

6
00:01:50,210 --> 00:01:50,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

7
00:01:51,650 --> 00:01:52,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hosts?</font>

8
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

9
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:55,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right!</font>

10
00:01:55,590 --> 00:01:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a host club we're on friendly 
terms with as a source of information,</font>

11
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but apparently, their whole
cast is down with some bug.</font>

12
00:02:02,390 --> 00:02:04,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They said they'd like our help.</font>

13
00:02:04,580 --> 00:02:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amateurs can't handle 
something like that.</font>

14
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, they said they'd 
teach us all that stuff.</font>

15
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We're talking about being hosts!</font>

16
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The place is called NOX.</font>

17
00:02:12,830 --> 00:02:13,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

18
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the place I worked at!</font>

19
00:02:15,530 --> 00:02:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

20
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my! Well, that speeds 
things up, doesn't it?</font>

21
00:02:24,350 --> 00:02:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Sero-chan! It's been so long!</font>

22
00:02:27,450 --> 00:02:28,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to see you!</font>

23
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never imagined you'd 
be working at Spirytus.</font>

24
00:02:31,790 --> 00:02:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was surprised, too!</font>

25
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:36,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know NOX 
was one of our regulars!</font>

26
00:02:36,580 --> 00:02:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a secret!</font>

27
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still...</font>

28
00:02:48,050 --> 00:02:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're absolutely wasted 
as torturers, aren't they?</font>

29
00:02:51,270 --> 00:02:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Owner, you're drooling.</font>

30
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:58,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, what do hosts do?</font>

31
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">T-Talk?</font>

32
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure we can just play it by ear.</font>

33
00:03:04,110 --> 00:03:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see I have no choice!</font>

34
00:03:06,110 --> 00:03:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that it's come to this,</font>

35
00:03:07,730 --> 00:03:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose I'll have to give a lecture.</font>

36
00:03:11,510 --> 00:03:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sero-san?!</font>

37
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no. It's Seroelle.</font>

38
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:18,010
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#1c1820">Name</font></b></font>

39
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:18,010
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#1c1820">Seroelle</font></b></font>

40
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wasn't there some other 
name you could use?</font>

41
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:21,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you'll need to be able to do the 
bare minimum of waiting on customers.</font>

42
00:03:21,470 --> 00:03:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think of me as a sweet young lady 
and practice, practice!</font>

43
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A sweet young lady?</font>

44
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure that's...</font>

45
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the only one who could...</font>

46
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm pretty cute, though!</font>

47
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have no shame.</font>

48
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:42,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello? Hurry up and get over here.</font>

49
00:03:42,070 --> 00:03:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right.</font>

50
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:47,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pleased to meet you!</font>

51
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Mike!</font>

52
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:52,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, what an adorable boy you are.</font>

53
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm Hugh.</font>

54
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:57,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, what an adorable boy you are.</font>

55
00:03:57,910 --> 00:04:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you have any other 
answers in your repertoire?</font>

56
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seroelle-san, what's your 
favorite torture implement?</font>

57
00:04:05,590 --> 00:04:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

58
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:11,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think about 
Torture Law Article 6, clause 3?</font>

59
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, stop that!</font>

60
00:04:12,210 --> 00:04:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Choose topics that are more likely 
to get a conversation going!</font>

61
00:04:16,010 --> 00:04:19,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This seems the most likely 
for lively conversation!</font>

62
00:04:19,280 --> 00:04:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly! You silly 
torture-brained idiots!</font>

63
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Refrain from talking about torture!</font>

64
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two can stick to smiling 
and nodding in conversation!</font>

65
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

66
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly. Good. Making drinks 
is part of a host's job.</font>

67
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd you make such a strong drink?!</font>

68
00:04:41,990 --> 00:04:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I should take 'em down fast.</font>

69
00:04:43,910 --> 00:04:46,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our guests are not meant 
to be taken down!</font>

70
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly!</font>

71
00:04:48,770 --> 00:04:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of you are just terrible!</font>

72
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch how I do it, okay?!</font>

73
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should've started with that.</font>

74
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-chan, you're cute!</font>

75
00:04:58,900 --> 00:05:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? I bet you say that to everyone.</font>

76
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:02,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

77
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:08,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But out of everyone... you're the cutest.</font>

78
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squee!</font>

79
00:05:14,050 --> 00:05:16,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hugh-chan, you said you're 
a university student, right?</font>

80
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

81
00:05:17,380 --> 00:05:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like torture studies,</font>

82
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I learn about torture methods 
and the basics of current law...</font>

83
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That's amazing.</font>

84
00:05:23,330 --> 00:05:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I'm boring you.</font>

85
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

86
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand all 
the complicated stuff,</font>

87
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but learning what you like...</font>

88
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is fun for me.</font>

89
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:35,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squee!</font>

90
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san is incredible.</font>

91
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mind if I have one, too?</font>

92
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

93
00:05:59,730 --> 00:06:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No better way to do naughty things 
than to do it with someone beautiful.</font>

94
00:06:04,260 --> 00:06:06,470
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="25"><font color="#191421">Wow...</font></font></font></b></font>

95
00:06:06,460 --> 00:06:10,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to be so grossed out! 
This level of cliché is good!</font>

96
00:06:06,470 --> 00:06:08,470
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="15">Wow...</font></font></b></font>

97
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, we're about to open!</font>

98
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

99
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And so...</i></font>

100
00:06:19,350 --> 00:06:21,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}And then, this is the incredible part...</font>

101
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the princes who had to dive 
straight into their challenge...</i></font>

102
00:06:24,420 --> 00:06:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>with their handsome faces and rookie
enthusiasm, managed to do quite well.</i></font>

103
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:26,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Thanks!</font>

104
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Miss, I can tell you're 
working really hard!</font>

105
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:31,820
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#1c1c17">Business hours have ended for the day.</font></b></font>

106
00:06:31,970 --> 00:06:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They drummed up a 
considerable amount of money.</i></font>

107
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How?</font>

108
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd this happen?</font>

109
00:06:41,420 --> 00:06:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for today!</font>

110
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been such a great help!</font>

111
00:06:45,220 --> 00:06:47,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And thanks to you, 
business was very good!</font>

112
00:06:46,050 --> 00:06:47,550
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font color="#f4e4c5">Packed House Bonus</font></b></font>

113
00:06:47,710 --> 00:06:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of you are well-suited to this.</font>

114
00:06:49,570 --> 00:06:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're all good at listening, so...</font>

115
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:55,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's the same sort of work, 
isn't being a host better?</font>

116
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd be welcome here!</font>

117
00:06:57,790 --> 00:07:00,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We prefer torture!</font>

118
00:07:01,910 --> 00:07:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so, the princes' night 
passed like a fleeting dream.</font>

119
00:07:07,730 --> 00:07:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hera-san?</font>

120
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But for it to end after just 
one time is such a shame.</font>

121
00:07:12,380 --> 00:07:15,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Host Club Spirytus. That could work.</font>

122
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it wouldn't.</font>

123
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:24,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so thirsty!</font>

124
00:07:26,340 --> 00:07:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this? I've never seen it before!</font>

125
00:07:28,260 --> 00:07:30,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No idea. It was just sitting here.</font>

126
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe it was left as a snack 
for us? I'll have some, too!</font>

127
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's sweet and bitter. 
What kind of juice is this?</font>

128
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?</font>

129
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This paper...</font>

130
00:07:49,690 --> 00:07:53,160
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="16"><font color="#271614">It's awful</font></font></font></b></font>

131
00:07:55,570 --> 00:07:59,580
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an7}<font color="#fefefc">m 0 0 l 130 0 130 50 0 50</font></font>

132
00:07:55,570 --> 00:07:59,580
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an7}<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3d3b3e">I made a fun 
new drug. 
Careful not 
to drink it.
-Izua</font></font></b></font>

133
00:08:05,710 --> 00:08:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that makes sense.</font>

134
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was one of Izu-san's compounds.</font>

135
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of weird drug is it this time?</font>

136
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:13,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

137
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! You've gotten smaller!</font>

138
00:08:22,820 --> 00:08:23,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How cute!</font>

139
00:08:23,890 --> 00:08:28,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, why haven't I changed 
at—Oh, you're so adorable!</font>

140
00:08:26,270 --> 00:08:28,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Calm down.</font>

141
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:29,940
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#353037">Safety First</font></b></font>

142
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:29,940
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#97363f">Let's stay safe today!</font></b></font>

143
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:32,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you're just 
seriously so cute, though!</font>

144
00:08:32,410 --> 00:08:35,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh! Cut it out! 
I'm still me on the inside.</font>

145
00:08:32,410 --> 00:08:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What is this? You're so adorable!</font>

146
00:08:37,300 --> 00:08:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder why Sero-san is the 
only one who's still the same.</font>

147
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's probably because I drank 
the prototype for this before.</font>

148
00:08:45,740 --> 00:08:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I built up some resistance.</font>

149
00:08:46,490 --> 00:08:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Izu-san!</font>

150
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I get it.</font>

151
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's what's going on.</font>

152
00:08:53,350 --> 00:08:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys, too?!</font>

153
00:08:57,450 --> 00:08:58,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

154
00:08:58,340 --> 00:09:01,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For now, I went and bought 
a bunch of kids' clothes.</font>

155
00:09:01,290 --> 00:09:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pick out whatever you like.</font>

156
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cute!</font>

157
00:09:11,090 --> 00:09:12,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with him?</font>

158
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:17,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san really likes small, 
cute creatures.</font>

159
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:23,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even you're cute.</font>

160
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it.</font>

161
00:09:25,330 --> 00:09:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should we do about 
the rest of our work?</font>

162
00:09:27,650 --> 00:09:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see.</font>

163
00:09:33,570 --> 00:09:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The optics are bad, 
so let's leave it for now.</font>

164
00:09:33,780 --> 00:09:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let go! Stop it!</font>

165
00:09:36,820 --> 00:09:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makes sense.</font>

166
00:09:37,470 --> 00:09:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey!</font>

167
00:09:40,650 --> 00:09:44,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now! The two of us will do our 
work just like we always do!</font>

168
00:09:44,090 --> 00:09:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This desk is so tall...</font>

169
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:51,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This turned into a real mess, didn't it?</font>

170
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're acting like it's not your problem.</font>

171
00:09:52,850 --> 00:09:55,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since we can't work, should we go home?</font>

172
00:09:55,220 --> 00:09:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since we have time, we thought 
we'd organize our paperwork.</font>

173
00:09:58,590 --> 00:09:59,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

174
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're both such good workers!</font>

175
00:10:01,210 --> 00:10:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if we went back to 
normal on the way home...</font>

176
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it could be a problem.</font>

177
00:10:06,460 --> 00:10:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

178
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:15,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All this concentrating 
has made me thirsty.</font>

179
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-chan! What do you want to drink?</font>

180
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm hungry, too.</font>

181
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:21,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should I go and buy for you?</font>

182
00:10:21,370 --> 00:10:23,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like eating something, too.</font>

183
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood!</font>

184
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything you like! Just name it!</font>

185
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go and buy it all!</font>

186
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're scaring me.</font>

187
00:10:31,310 --> 00:10:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

188
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:36,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's so adorable when 
someone cute is happy!</font>

189
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

190
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on! This love 
is the purest of pure!</font>

191
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

192
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:57,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#392b33">GRIND</font></b></font></font>

193
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:57,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#392b33">GRIND</font></b></font></font>

194
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:57,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#392b33">GRIND</font></b></font></font>

195
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:57,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#392b33">GRIND</font></b></font></font>

196
00:10:53,210 --> 00:10:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Infuriating.</font>

197
00:10:55,660 --> 00:10:58,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With only a child's strength, 
that doesn't hurt!</font>

198
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't forget this.</font>

199
00:11:04,130 --> 00:11:06,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're back!</font>

200
00:11:06,250 --> 00:11:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's such a relief.</font>

201
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:10,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've had enough of 
that guy's experiments.</font>

202
00:11:10,810 --> 00:11:13,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say that, but you'll 
drink them again, right?</font>

203
00:11:14,300 --> 00:11:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait.</font>

204
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone's so big.</font>

205
00:11:20,650 --> 00:11:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've turned tiny.</font>

206
00:11:24,400 --> 00:11:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

207
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is the timing only different for me?!</font>

208
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe your resistance only delayed 
the onset of the effects.</font>

209
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should make it not work at all!</font>

210
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess it's my turn to 
take care of you now.</font>

211
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! He's abducting me!</font>

212
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for all your hard work!</font>

213
00:11:44,570 --> 00:11:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if it's just your outward appearance,</font>

214
00:11:47,030 --> 00:11:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's dangerous for a kid to go home alone.</font>

215
00:11:50,290 --> 00:11:52,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa, you're so nice!</font>

216
00:11:52,070 --> 00:11:53,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Sero-kun?</font>

217
00:11:53,970 --> 00:11:55,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-kun, is that you?</font>

218
00:11:55,730 --> 00:11:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

219
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up. We're having dinner.</font>

220
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

221
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:04,820
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#281f2a">Back to
 normal</font></font></b></font>

222
00:12:04,980 --> 00:12:08,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might be happy being 
a kid in Siu-san's house.</font>

223
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:10,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it okay if I stay the night?</font>

224
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out.</font>

225
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:14,960
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#fefefe">The <font color="#9714eb">D<font color="#fefefe">aily <font color="#eee43d">L<font color="#fefefe">ife of a <font color="#eee43d">P<font color="#fefefe">art-Time <font color="#9714eb">T<font color="#fefefe">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

226
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:17,960
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#0b0a0c">The <font color="#695770">D<font color="#0b0a0c">aily <font color="#37c2a3">L<font color="#0b0a0c">ife of a <font color="#c8baca">P<font color="#0b0a0c">art-Time <font color="#2c64d9">T<font color="#0b0a0c">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

227
00:12:19,920 --> 00:12:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking of which,</font>

228
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when they teach us something...</font>

229
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we pair up like this a lot, don't we?</font>

230
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:30,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of teaching 
style does Siu-san have?</font>

231
00:12:32,210 --> 00:12:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's very detailed in his instructions,
and it's easy to understand.</font>

232
00:12:35,070 --> 00:12:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about Sero-san?</font>

233
00:12:36,350 --> 00:12:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the same! Sero-san 
is really good at teaching!</font>

234
00:12:40,850 --> 00:12:44,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is? I might be a little curious now.</font>

235
00:12:44,220 --> 00:12:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know! In that case...</font>

236
00:12:48,460 --> 00:12:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

237
00:12:50,130 --> 00:12:53,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can we try pairing up differently 
than we usually do?</font>

238
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:55,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! That sounds like fun!</font>

239
00:12:55,430 --> 00:12:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind either way.</font>

240
00:12:59,460 --> 00:13:02,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, go ahead and give it a good whabam.</font>

241
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A "whabam"?</font>

242
00:13:04,230 --> 00:13:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

243
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And after that, it's okay 
to be more like, "pyaa"!</font>

244
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Pyaa"?</font>

245
00:13:15,350 --> 00:13:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you count the breaths?</font>

246
00:13:18,310 --> 00:13:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... just a general idea.</font>

247
00:13:21,090 --> 00:13:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heart rate, pupil dilation, 
angle of the head...</font>

248
00:13:23,830 --> 00:13:25,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all important.</font>

249
00:13:25,970 --> 00:13:27,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to check everything 
at this stage.</font>

250
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, sir.</font>

251
00:13:34,290 --> 00:13:40,130
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#1c141e">Theory-Based</font></b></font>

252
00:13:34,290 --> 00:13:40,130
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#1c141e">Intuition-Based</font></b></font>

253
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}He was so hard to understand.</i></font>

254
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:39,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}He was so hard to teach.</i></font>

255
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:51,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san!</font>

256
00:13:53,250 --> 00:13:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was organizing the 
shelves and found this.</font>

257
00:13:56,450 --> 00:13:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that brings back memories!</font>

258
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this the two of you 
from a long time ago?</font>

259
00:14:01,670 --> 00:14:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

260
00:14:03,230 --> 00:14:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your hair looks sort of 
like Siu-san's back then.</font>

261
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way it goes like this.</font>

262
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that.</font>

263
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because if I tuck my hair back 
when I'm working, I get blood on my face.</font>

264
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:16,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a practical thing?!</font>

265
00:14:16,220 --> 00:14:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you copied him 
because you look up to him.</font>

266
00:14:19,220 --> 00:14:20,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to do it, too?</font>

267
00:14:20,950 --> 00:14:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm okay like this.</font>

268
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got blood on your face again.</font>

269
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:34,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I didn't notice.</font>

270
00:14:34,460 --> 00:14:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just can't fix that habit, huh?</font>

271
00:14:38,190 --> 00:14:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I'll do my hair like yours, then.</font>

272
00:14:41,210 --> 00:14:43,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That way, my hair won't fall down.</font>

273
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's creepy.</font>

274
00:14:44,770 --> 00:14:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so mean.</font>

275
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which reason was it?</font>

276
00:14:59,530 --> 00:15:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good mor...ning?</font>

277
00:15:03,010 --> 00:15:04,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san?!</font>

278
00:15:04,300 --> 00:15:04,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

279
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, your hair is sort of... cute today.</font>

280
00:15:13,170 --> 00:15:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was them.</font>

281
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're forgetting your recorders.</font>

282
00:15:16,350 --> 00:15:17,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

283
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa, I'll do your hair for you!</font>

284
00:15:20,630 --> 00:15:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There. All done.</font>

285
00:15:22,850 --> 00:15:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

286
00:15:24,530 --> 00:15:26,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're good at this. And fast.</font>

287
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem used to it.</font>

288
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you pleased with my work?</font>

289
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:34,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I actually really like drying hair 
and braiding it and stuff.</font>

290
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

291
00:15:36,470 --> 00:15:38,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">something that'd snag the ladies, too.</font>

292
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The poor things.</font>

293
00:15:39,560 --> 00:15:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it. You make it sound 
like I'm a con artist.</font>

294
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's Von-san!</i></font>

295
00:15:52,050 --> 00:15:54,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll go and say hi.</i></font>

296
00:15:54,260 --> 00:15:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Von-san!</font>

297
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This really is high-quality stuff, right?</font>

298
00:15:58,090 --> 00:16:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, of course. I prepared 
first-class goods for you.</font>

299
00:16:01,630 --> 00:16:04,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There've been adulterated 
mixtures making the rounds lately.</font>

300
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we've known each other 
a while, so I'll trust you.</font>

301
00:16:08,490 --> 00:16:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for your business.</font>

302
00:16:13,250 --> 00:16:15,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what happened.</font>

303
00:16:15,540 --> 00:16:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Von-san is a scary person, isn't he?</font>

304
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

305
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

306
00:16:21,710 --> 00:16:23,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're only realizing that now?</font>

307
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mi-chan! Chi-chan!</font>

308
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home!</font>

309
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bought you some really good food!</font>

310
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:40,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eat it all up, okay?</font>

311
00:16:47,220 --> 00:16:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san.</font>

312
00:16:48,940 --> 00:16:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want to do 
about dinner today?</font>

313
00:16:51,040 --> 00:16:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. What should we do?</font>

314
00:16:54,040 --> 00:16:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san, are you guys 
having a sleepover?</font>

315
00:16:57,060 --> 00:16:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. We have work that'll 
go late into the night.</font>

316
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Can we join you, too?</font>

317
00:17:03,410 --> 00:17:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why?</font>

318
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do realize that I know...</font>

319
00:17:07,790 --> 00:17:12,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that every once in a while, you two 
eat really good late-night snacks!</font>

320
00:17:15,040 --> 00:17:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you think I hadn't noticed?</font>

321
00:17:18,230 --> 00:17:21,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those aromas that occasionally 
linger in the kitchenette...</font>

322
00:17:18,600 --> 00:17:22,140
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an7}<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#f0f0f0">Lingering aroma of
 delicious late-night snacks</font></font></b></font>

323
00:17:21,470 --> 00:17:23,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't fool my nose!</font>

324
00:17:24,210 --> 00:17:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We make food sometimes, that's all.</font>

325
00:17:26,520 --> 00:17:29,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna eat some! I wanna 
eat some! I wanna eat some!</font>

326
00:17:29,700 --> 00:17:31,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hugh, you want to eat 
some, too, don't you?</font>

327
00:17:31,650 --> 00:17:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I'm curious.</font>

328
00:17:33,410 --> 00:17:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most of the time, we go out to eat 
or make do with ready-made.</font>

329
00:17:36,830 --> 00:17:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please cook something this time.</font>

330
00:17:39,050 --> 00:17:41,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san, what do you want to do?</font>

331
00:17:41,430 --> 00:17:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not a bad idea for them to get 
experience with how we do things at night.</font>

332
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, I guess...</font>

333
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we go shopping?</font>

334
00:17:49,420 --> 00:17:50,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

335
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you going to make?</font>

336
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ramen and fried rice.</font>

337
00:17:57,750 --> 00:17:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

338
00:17:59,520 --> 00:18:01,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Set your expectations high!</font>

339
00:18:01,290 --> 00:18:03,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san's cooking is really good!</font>

340
00:18:06,390 --> 00:18:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are four of us today,</font>

341
00:18:08,330 --> 00:18:10,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I guess I'll add more 
toppings than usual.</font>

342
00:18:10,770 --> 00:18:12,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

343
00:18:18,220 --> 00:18:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you two cook at all?</font>

344
00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always get delivery.</font>

345
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My mom always makes food for me.</font>

346
00:18:25,450 --> 00:18:26,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you, Sero-san?</font>

347
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most of the time, I eat out 
or get it ready-made,</font>

348
00:18:29,460 --> 00:18:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if I watch a video or look 
at a recipe, I can usually make it.</font>

349
00:18:32,460 --> 00:18:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow. You're so talented.</font>

350
00:18:35,320 --> 00:18:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I cook something...</font>

351
00:18:37,380 --> 00:18:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's usually because I saw something 
and thought it looked good,</font>

352
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or someone asked me to make something.</font>

353
00:18:43,150 --> 00:18:44,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

354
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I want to eat home-cooked food,</font>

355
00:18:46,340 --> 00:18:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I visit my parents' house...</font>

356
00:18:48,050 --> 00:18:52,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Siu-san, I want some 
of your rolled omelets!</font>

357
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:50,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or I go freeload at Siu-san's place.</font>

358
00:18:50,870 --> 00:18:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you a stray dog or something?</font>

359
00:18:52,120 --> 00:18:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Buy some eggs and bring them back here.</font>

360
00:18:54,610 --> 00:18:56,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

361
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've already chopped all this up?</font>

362
00:18:58,520 --> 00:19:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's amazing!</font>

363
00:19:01,550 --> 00:19:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can do it, too, you know.</font>

364
00:19:03,380 --> 00:19:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

365
00:19:03,670 --> 00:19:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop making it a competition.</font>

366
00:19:05,900 --> 00:19:08,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cooking looks difficult.</font>

367
00:19:08,870 --> 00:19:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's easy. Wanna try?</font>

368
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes!</font>

369
00:19:20,970 --> 00:19:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's actually amazing!</font>

370
00:19:24,590 --> 00:19:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

371
00:19:26,090 --> 00:19:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. Don't worry about it!</font>

372
00:19:28,810 --> 00:19:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just about ready, 
so you two go sit and wait.</font>

373
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:34,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

374
00:19:34,340 --> 00:19:37,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been sent to the bench.</font>

375
00:19:38,820 --> 00:19:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san, do you like cooking because 
you have Leu-chan and Nero-chan?</font>

376
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

377
00:19:45,490 --> 00:19:46,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before that,</font>

378
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was always around some people 
who were careless about their food.</font>

379
00:19:50,490 --> 00:19:52,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used to cook for them a lot.</font>

380
00:19:52,940 --> 00:19:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. So that's why this place 
is so well-stocked, huh?</font>

381
00:19:55,250 --> 00:20:01,970
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="12"><font color="#666974">Real
 Mirin</font></font></font></b></font>

382
00:19:55,250 --> 00:20:01,970
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="10"><font color="#454a51">Cooking Sake</font></font></font>

383
00:19:55,250 --> 00:20:01,970
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="12"><font color="#4a4c55">Soup Base</font></font></b></font></font>

384
00:19:57,520 --> 00:20:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we've got gluttons 
like you around, too.</font>

385
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:01,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Much appreciated.</font>

386
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:04,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, what a wonderful smell!</font>

387
00:20:04,830 --> 00:20:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're still here?</font>

388
00:20:06,230 --> 00:20:09,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A tricky negotiation took 
longer than expected.</font>

389
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I'm famished.</font>

390
00:20:10,970 --> 00:20:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to eat here?</font>

391
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't mind?</font>

392
00:20:13,370 --> 00:20:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No problem.</font>

393
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:15,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much.</font>

394
00:20:15,930 --> 00:20:17,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make more noodles!</font>

395
00:20:20,350 --> 00:20:23,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't just stand there. 
Set the table, moron!</font>

396
00:20:23,660 --> 00:20:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you calling me a moron?!</font>

397
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no, we'll set the table!</font>

398
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:30,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now...</font>

399
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:32,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to eat!</font>

400
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:36,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is delicious! Like it 
came from a restaurant!</font>

401
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love this flavor!</font>

402
00:20:40,540 --> 00:20:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san, this ramen is delicious!</font>

403
00:20:42,620 --> 00:20:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, moron! I'm the one 
who made the ramen!</font>

404
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You—</font>

405
00:20:46,710 --> 00:20:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even so... it's still delicious.</font>

406
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good to be honest.</font>

407
00:20:51,910 --> 00:20:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As usual, it's delicious.</font>

408
00:20:54,430 --> 00:20:56,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We three used to eat it a lot, huh?</font>

409
00:20:56,370 --> 00:20:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, we did.</font>

410
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:01,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's good, huh?</font>

411
00:21:01,010 --> 00:21:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never thought we'd ever 
have a day as lively as this.</font>

412
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah!</font>

413
00:21:04,760 --> 00:21:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think you're doing?!</font>

414
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:08,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's true.</font>

415
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:13,410
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#303030">Let's build a <font color="#ea3574">fun, 
cheerful <font color="#303030">workplace together!</font></font></font></b></font>

416
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:13,410
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#dffedf">Stop harassment!</font></b></font>

417
00:21:13,620 --> 00:21:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for the meal!</font>

418
00:21:17,040 --> 00:21:18,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so full.</font>

419
00:21:18,990 --> 00:21:20,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, now.</font>

420
00:21:20,270 --> 00:21:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have work after this, 
and you even had seconds.</font>

421
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to get sleepy...</font>

422
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh.</font>

423
00:21:35,910 --> 00:21:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These kids sure need a lot 
of looking after, don't they?</font>

424
00:21:38,630 --> 00:21:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They really do.</font>

425
00:21:41,230 --> 00:21:43,400
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#161319">The Next Day</font></b></font>

426
00:21:41,840 --> 00:21:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for falling asleep last night!</font>

427
00:21:46,330 --> 00:21:48,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys were out cold.</font>

428
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

429
00:21:50,320 --> 00:21:53,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess we can't give you 
night work for a while yet.</font>

430
00:21:53,260 --> 00:21:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not until you handle yourselves better.</font>

431
00:21:55,760 --> 00:21:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We really are still awful 
at this, aren't we?</font>

432
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll work even harder from now on 
to make sure we'll be able to do it.</font>

433
00:22:04,370 --> 00:22:07,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All so that we can eat at 
the Spirytus Diner again!</font>

434
00:22:07,300 --> 00:22:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, yes!</font>

435
00:22:08,730 --> 00:22:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's</i> your reason?</font>

436
00:22:38,210 --> 00:22:45,590
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="12"><b><font color="#eff0f3">{\an9}Translator:
Timer:
Editor:
Quality Control:
Final Quality Control:</font></b></font></font>

437
